Package: jamma
Title: MA-plots for omics data
Version: 0.0.38.900
Authors@R: person("James", "Ward", email="jmw86069@gmail.com", role=c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create MA-plots with specific control samples,
    using centering groups as relevant to experiment design.
    Volcano plots with hit filtering by gene.
    All plots use smooth scatter plots to visualize a large
    number of points efficiently, thereby revealing proper point
    density.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: jamba (>= 1.0.2),
    grDevices,
    methods,
    colorjam,
    matrixStats,
    ggplot2,
    ggh4x,
    withr,
    cli
